In English and Spanish; Spanish text not printed.
                        Ratification advised by the Senate, with reservation, Mar. 13, 1925;
                        ratified by the President Mar. 23, 1925; ratified by Cuba Mar. 18, 1925;
                        ratifications exchanged at Washington, Mar. 23, 1925; proclaimed by the
                        President Mar. 24, 1925.
